  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168390/extras/a5b27d593efba1ada9d52bfc4546fdef.avif?t=1740747919\" width=620 height=180 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >An AMAZING and RELAXING game!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <i>Work Adventure</i>, you have complete freedom to do whatever you want! Whether you're watching a video or podcast, working, or even studying, keep the game open in the background and enjoy! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168390/extras/95132b60dda65924a34a60beafe5dcec.poster.avif?t=1740747919\" width=620 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168390/extras/95132b60dda65924a34a60beafe5dcec.webm?t=1740747919\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168390/extras/95132b60dda65924a34a60beafe5dcec.mp4?t=1740747919\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >LOTS OF COMBAT!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >FIGHT against CREATURES and COLLECT EXCLUSIVE items! In EARLY ACCESS, there will be 7 groups of creatures, each group containing at least two creatures, each with 3 to 6 VARIATIONS! So many cute monsters!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168390/extras/0a1c863fb6c8ab6f0a150bccf4be1aa6.poster.avif?t=1740747919\" width=620 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168390/extras/0a1c863fb6c8ab6f0a150bccf4be1aa6.webm?t=1740747919\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168390/extras/0a1c863fb6c8ab6f0a150bccf4be1aa6.mp4?t=1740747919\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PARENTS ARE THE ONES WHO RAISE!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For the soft-hearted, it's also possible to TAMED the creatures using items acquired in the GAME! So fill up your backpack and capture all the little creatures, okay? But remember, they have SPECIFIC TIMES and ITEMS for their capture!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168390/extras/c2b0839180080713e666dcc18bf99024.poster.avif?t=1740747919\" width=620 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168390/extras/c2b0839180080713e666dcc18bf99024.webm?t=1740747919\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168390/extras/c2b0839180080713e666dcc18bf99024.mp4?t=1740747919\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WHO AM I?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I'm Davi, better known as DevBandeira on social media (YouTube, Udemy, etc.), Developer/Game Designer, and even Web Developer for this project.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I decided to create <i>Work Adventure</i> inspired by other games in this genre, aiming to bring elements of monster and creature collection games, as well as direct combat with the little monsters, attributes and resources, collectible items, and much more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168390/extras/16fafb32903e85a4d6cd16918bbccba6.avif?t=1740747919\" width=620 height=180 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168390/extras/a5b27d593efba1ada9d52bfc4546fdef.avif?t=1740747919\" width=620 height=180 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >An AMAZING and RELAXING game!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <i>Work Adventure</i>, you have complete freedom to do whatever you want! Whether you're watching a video or podcast, working, or even studying, keep the game open in the background and enjoy! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168390/extras/95132b60dda65924a34a60beafe5dcec.poster.avif?t=1740747919\" width=620 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168390/extras/95132b60dda65924a34a60beafe5dcec.webm?t=1740747919\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168390/extras/95132b60dda65924a34a60beafe5dcec.mp4?t=1740747919\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >LOTS OF COMBAT!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >FIGHT against CREATURES and COLLECT EXCLUSIVE items! In EARLY ACCESS, there will be 7 groups of creatures, each group containing at least two creatures, each with 3 to 6 VARIATIONS! So many cute monsters!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168390/extras/0a1c863fb6c8ab6f0a150bccf4be1aa6.poster.avif?t=1740747919\" width=620 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168390/extras/0a1c863fb6c8ab6f0a150bccf4be1aa6.webm?t=1740747919\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168390/extras/0a1c863fb6c8ab6f0a150bccf4be1aa6.mp4?t=1740747919\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PARENTS ARE THE ONES WHO RAISE!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For the soft-hearted, it's also possible to TAMED the creatures using items acquired in the GAME! So fill up your backpack and capture all the little creatures, okay? But remember, they have SPECIFIC TIMES and ITEMS for their capture!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168390/extras/c2b0839180080713e666dcc18bf99024.poster.avif?t=1740747919\" width=620 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168390/extras/c2b0839180080713e666dcc18bf99024.webm?t=1740747919\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168390/extras/c2b0839180080713e666dcc18bf99024.mp4?t=1740747919\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WHO AM I?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I'm Davi, better known as DevBandeira on social media (YouTube, Udemy, etc.), Developer/Game Designer, and even Web Developer for this project.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I decided to create <i>Work Adventure</i> inspired by other games in this genre, aiming to bring elements of monster and creature collection games, as well as direct combat with the little monsters, attributes and resources, collectible items, and much more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168390/extras/16fafb32903e85a4d6cd16918bbccba6.avif?t=1740747919\" width=620 height=180 /></span></p>",
